headline.main: Poland Names Counter-Candidate to Tusk as EU Leader
headline.print_headline: Poland Names Counter-Candidate to Tusk as EU Leader

lead_paragraph: Poland on Saturday proposed a counter-candidate to Donald Tusk as European Council head, saying the Polish incumbent has hurt his country's interests.
